data.meta_description: The modern adventures across space and time - from Christopher Eccleston to Jodie Whittaker. Its the trip of a lifetime.
data.text:
1. Rose

Rose Tyler meets a mysterious stranger called the Doctor, and realises Earth is in danger.

44 mins

2. The End of the World

The Doctor takes Rose on her first voyage through time, to the year five billion.

45 mins

3. The Unquiet Dead

Charles Dickens and the Doctor team up as corpses stalk the streets of Victorian Cardiff.

45 mins

4. Aliens of London

Rose is taken home, but a spaceship crashes in the Thames and London is closed off.

45 mins

5. World War Three

Time is running out for the Doctor as Downing Street announces an Interplanetary War.

43 mins

7. The Long Game

The Doctor investigates a strange satellite, and Adam's skills as an assistant are tested.

44 mins

9. The Empty Child

Homeless children in wartime London are terrorised by an unearthly child.

42 mins

10. The Doctor Dances

The Child's plague is spreading through wartime London and its zombie army is on the march

43 mins

11. Boom Town

The Doctor discovers a Slitheen is behind a plan to build a power station in Cardiff.

43 mins

12. Bad Wolf

The Doctor, Rose and Captain Jack have to fight for their lives on board the Game Station.

43 mins

13. The Parting of the Ways

The ninth Doctor's final episode is an epic encounter with the Daleks.

46 mins
